         <div class="AccordionPanel"> 
          <div class="AccordionPanelTab"> 
           <h2>WDS and WDM Exam Reference Materials</h2> 
          </div> 
          <div class="AccordionPanelContent" style="height: 1090px"> 
           <div class="intro"> 
            <p><b>Water Distribution Specialist (WDS) and Water Distribution Manager (WDM) Exam Reference Materials</b></p> 
            <p>Below are approved reference sources for the ABC WDS and WDM exams. Operators should use the latest edition of these reference sources to prepare for the exam.</p> 
           </div> 
           <div class="reference-list"> 
            <!-- START OF REFERENCE MATERIAL --> 
            <div class="reference-item"> 
             <h3>American Water Works Association (AWWA)</h3> 
             <ul> 
              <li>Water Transmission and Distribution</li> 
              <li>Water Distribution Operator Training Handbook</li> 
              <li>Basic Science Concepts and Applications</li> 
              <li>Water System Security, A Field Guide</li> 
              <li>Water Quality</li> 
             </ul> 
             <p><b>To order, contact:</b><br> AWWA<br> 6666 West Quincy Avenue<br> Denver, CO 80235<br> Web Site: <a target="_blank" href="http://www.awwa.org/"> www.awwa.org</a><br> Phone: 800-926-7337</p> 
            </div> 
            <!-- END OF REFERENCE MATERIAL --> 
            <!-- START OF REFERENCE MATERIAL --> 
            <div class="reference-item"> 
             <h3>Association of State Drinking Water Administrators (ASDWA)</h3> 
             <ul> 
              <li>Security Vulnerability Self Assessment Guide for Small Drinking Water Systems</li> 
             </ul> 
             <p><b>To order, contact:</b><br> ASDWA<br> 1401 Wilson Blvd Suite 1225<br> Arlington, VA 22209<br> Web Site: <a target="_blank" href="http://www.asdwa.org/"> www.asdwa.org</a><br> Phone: 703-812-9505</p> 
            </div> 
            <!-- END OF REFERENCE MATERIAL --> 
            <!-- START OF REFERENCE MATERIAL --> 
            <div class="reference-item"> 
             <h3>California State University, Sacramento (CSUS)</h3> 
             <ul> 
              <li>Water Distribution System Operation and Maintenance</li> 
              <li>Small Water System Operation and Maintenance</li> 
              <li>Water Treatment Plant Operation, Volumes I and II</li> 
              <li>Utility Management</li> 
              <li>Manage for Success</li> 
             </ul> 
             <p><b>To order, contact:</b><br> CSUS<br> Office of Water Programs<br> 6000 J Street<br> Sacramento, CA 95819-6025<br> Web Site: <a target="_blank" href="http://www.owp.csus.edu/"> www.owp.csus.edu</a><br> Phone: 916-278-6142</p> 
            </div> 
